===Religion===
{{Main|Religion in Cyprus}}
{{double image|left|Kykko Monastery 2.jpg|180|Larnaca 01-2017 img30 Salt Lake.jpg|180|[[Kykkos Monastery]] in [[Pedoulas]] (left) and [[Hala Sultan Tekke]] near [[Larnaca Salt Lake]] (right).}}
{{bar box
|title=[[Religion in Cyprus]] ([[Pew Research Center|Pew Research]])<ref name=pew>[http://www.globalreligiousfutures.org/countries/cyprus/religious_demography#/?affiliations_religion_id=0&affiliations_year=2010 Pew Research Center's Religion & Public Life Project: Cyprus]. [[Pew Research Center]]. 2010.</ref><ref name="CIA">{{cite web |url=https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/geos/cy.html |title=Cyprus |work=[[The World Factbook]] |publisher=[[Central Intelligence Agency]] |accessdate=9 February 2010}}</ref>
|titlebar=#ddd
