'''Gairidhara''' ({{lang-ne|गैह्री धारा}}) is a residential area of [[Kathmandu]], the capital city of [[Nepal]]. It borders the [[Narayanhity Palace]], [[Lazimpat]] and [[Baluwatar, Kathmandu|Baluwatar]] and is just 20 minutes away from what is known as the downtown of Kathmandu, Newroad and Ason.
